---
import Card from './Card.astro';
const { posts } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="blog-grid">
  <p>I've always toyed around with keeping a blog, but it's never stuck. This year, I've set a personal goal to write one post every week, posting on Sunday.</p>
  <p>I'm hoping to improve my writing skills while sharing some of my thoughts and experiences from the past week.</p>
  <p>Let's see if I can stick to it...</p>
  <div class="post-list">
    {await Promise.all(posts.map(async (post) => {
      return (
        <Card
          blog={true}
          newTab={false}
          title={post.data.title}
          description={post.data.snippet}
          url={`/blog/${post.slug}/`}
          date={new Date(post.data.pubDate).toLocaleDateString("en-us", {
              year: "numeric",
              month: "short",
              day: "numeric",
            })}
            tags={post.data.tags}
        />
      );
    }))}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .post-snippet-wrap {
    display: flex;
  }
  .post-img {
    border-radius: 100%;
    height: 100px;
    float: left;
    margin: 1rem 1rem 0 0;
  }  
  .post-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .post-title-link {
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .post-title-wrap {
    display: flex;
    border-bottom: 3px dashed var(--border-color);
    justify-content: space-between;
    column-gap: .5rem;
  }
  .post-title-link {
    display: block;
  }
  .post-title {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-color);
    text-align: left;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .post-date {
    margin: 5px 0 0;
    color: var(--text-color);
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 1rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
    align-self: flex-end;
  }
  .post-continue {
    display: inline;
    text-decoration: underline;
    opacity: .75;
    transition: all .125s;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .post-continue:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .tag {
    background-color: var(--tag-bg-color);
    color: var(--tag-text-color);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .post-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .post-list-item {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>